[h3 id=Comments 
	" Comments
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"The main objective of the run is to collect the required ability items and get back to the Lab in order to access the final two levels of the game. However, one of the ability items, the Dynamo, which is required to open the door to the Lab (and is also used against the final boss), requires 2000 Gems in order to be obtained. As a result, gems are collected throughout the run. The gem route mainly collects Purple, Yellow and Cyan gems (worth 5, 10 and 25 respectively), with reds and greens being collected less frequently.
	$LF
]p
[h3 id=Tricks 
	"Tricks
	$LF
]h3
[h4 id=QuickTurnaround 
	" Quick Turnaround
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"The fastest way to turn around is to press opposite to the direction Spyro is currently facing - e.g. if facing Up, pressing Down will turn to the side faster than pressing Left or Right.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=HoverJump 
	" Hover Jump
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"This is done by pressing A twice in mid-air. This is used to jump up walls or steps which are 2 blocks high.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=QuickEscape 
	" Quick Escape
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"This ability is used in order to return to Dragon Shores quickly. It is used in Fairy Library, Rabbit Habitat and Moneybags Mansion once the required gems/items have been obtained.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=Fence-Walking 
	" Fence-Walking
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Fences are 3 blocks high, so you normally cannot jump on top of them. However, by standing on higher ground is is possible to get on top of certain fences. This allows shortcuts in Thieve's Guild and Chateau Ripto.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=WindBreathHover 
	" Wind Breath Hover
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"By using Wind Breath and pressing B once every 30 frames, Spyro can hover on air after going over an edge. This is used to skip the Ripto battle in Dragon Shores.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=ChateauRiptoStatueSkip 
	" Chateau Ripto Statue Skip
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"The statue in this level normally has to be destroyed using a Bomb Egg in order to proceed. However, the wall behind it is lower than it looks, so I can get up it just by hover jumping behind the statue.
	$LF
]p
[h3 id=Stagebystagecomments 
	" Stage by stage comments
	$LF
]h3
[h4 id=FairyLibrary 
	" Fairy Library
	$LF
]h4
[p 
