	$LF
]p
[h4 id=YetiSerengeti 
	" Yeti Serengeti
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Burning Ripto banners or baskets inside a dark cave causes a lot of lag.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=RabbitHabitat 
	" Rabbit Habitat
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"You cannot charge or jump while towing one of the magician's 'halves'... Quick Escape to return to Dragon Shores.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=BananaSavannah 
